name: USCongressionalMidtermElectionFactSkill
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: midterm election facts
des: This Alexa skill will allow to learn over 150 facts about midterm congressional elections for the House of Representatives in the USA since 1950. Simply say "Alexa, open midterm election facts" to get started. Then ask Alexa to tell you midterm election facts until your heart is content. Information summarizing both national and state-level information about midterm elections for the House are provided.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
